{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'm going to begin by reciting a poem."},{"time":5000,"text":"\"Oh beloved dentist:"},{"time":7000,"text":"Your rubber fingers in my mouth ..."},{"time":10000,"text":"your voice so soft and muffled ..."},{"time":14000,"text":"Lower the mask, dear dentist,"},{"time":16000,"text":"lower the mask.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"Okay, in this presentation,"},{"time":23000,"text":"I'm going to be putting the right side of your brains"},{"time":25000,"text":"through a fairly serious workout."},{"time":27000,"text":"You're going to see a lot of imagery,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and it's not always connected to what I'm talking about,"},{"time":32000,"text":"so I need you to kind of split your brains in half"},{"time":35000,"text":"and let the images flow over one side"},{"time":38000,"text":"and listen to me on the other."},{"time":40000,"text":"So I am one of those people"},{"time":42000,"text":"with a transformative personal story."},{"time":45000,"text":"Six years ago,"},{"time":47000,"text":"after 20 years in graphic design and typography,"},{"time":50000,"text":"I changed the way I was working"},{"time":52000,"text":"and the way most graphic designers work"},{"time":55000,"text":"to pursue a more personal approach to my work,"},{"time":60000,"text":"with only the humble attempt"},{"time":62000,"text":"to simply make a living doing something that I loved."},{"time":66000,"text":"But something weird happened."},{"time":69000,"text":"I became bizarrely"},{"time":71000,"text":"popular."},{"time":73000,"text":"My current work"},{"time":75000,"text":"seems to resonate with people"},{"time":77000,"text":"in a way that has so taken me by surprise"},{"time":80000,"text":"that I still frequently wonder"},{"time":82000,"text":"what in the hell is going on."},{"time":84000,"text":"And I'm slowly coming to understand"},{"time":86000,"text":"that the appeal of what I do"},{"time":88000,"text":"may be connected to why I do it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"These days, I call myself a graphic artist."},{"time":96000,"text":"So where my work as a graphic designer"},{"time":99000,"text":"was to follow strategy,"},{"time":101000,"text":"my work now"},{"time":103000,"text":"follows my heart"},{"time":105000,"text":"and my interests"},{"time":107000,"text":"with the guidance of my ego"},{"time":110000,"text":"to create work that is mutually beneficial to myself and a client."},{"time":114000,"text":"Now, this is heresy"},{"time":116000,"text":"in the design world."},{"time":118000,"text":"The ego is not supposed"},{"time":120000,"text":"to be involved in graphic design."},{"time":123000,"text":"But I find that for myself,"},{"time":125000,"text":"without exception,"},{"time":127000,"text":"the more I deal with the work"},{"time":129000,"text":"as something of my own,"},{"time":131000,"text":"as something that is personal,"},{"time":133000,"text":"the more successful it is"},{"time":135000,"text":"as something that's compelling,"},{"time":138000,"text":"interesting and sustaining."},{"time":141000,"text":"So I exist somewhat outside of the mainstream"},{"time":143000,"text":"of design thinking."},{"time":145000,"text":"Where others might look at measurable results,"},{"time":148000,"text":"I tend to be interested in more ethereal qualities,"},{"time":151000,"text":"like \"Does it bring joy?\""},{"time":153000,"text":"\"Is there a sense of wonder?\""},{"time":155000,"text":"and \"Does it invoke curiosity?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":158000,"text":"This is a scientific diagram, by the way."},{"time":161000,"text":"I don't have time to explain it,"},{"time":163000,"text":"but it has to do with DNA and RNA."},{"time":166000,"text":"So I have a particular imaginative approach to visual work."},{"time":169000,"text":"The things that interest me when I'm working"},{"time":172000,"text":"are visual structure,"},{"time":174000,"text":"surprise"},{"time":176000,"text":"and anything that requires figuring things out."},{"time":179000,"text":"So for this reason, I'm particularly drawn"},{"time":181000,"text":"to systems and patterns."},{"time":184000,"text":"I'm going to give you a couple of examples of how my brain works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187000,"text":"This is a piece that I did for"},{"time":189000,"text":"The Guardian newspaper in the U.K."},{"time":191000,"text":"They have a magazine that they call G2."},{"time":195000,"text":"And this is for their puzzle special"},{"time":197000,"text":"in 2007."},{"time":199000,"text":"And puzzling it is."},{"time":201000,"text":"I started by creating a series of tiling units."},{"time":204000,"text":"And these tiling units, I designed"},{"time":206000,"text":"specifically so that they would contain"},{"time":208000,"text":"parts of letterforms within their shapes"},{"time":211000,"text":"so that I could then"},{"time":213000,"text":"join those pieces together"},{"time":215000,"text":"to create letters and then words"},{"time":217000,"text":"within the abstract patterning."},{"time":220000,"text":"But then as well, I was able to"},{"time":222000,"text":"just flip them, rotate them"},{"time":224000,"text":"and combine them in different ways"},{"time":226000,"text":"to create either regular patterns"},{"time":228000,"text":"or abstract patterns."},{"time":231000,"text":"So here's the word puzzle again."},{"time":234000,"text":"And here it is with the abstract surrounding."},{"time":237000,"text":"And as you can see, it's extremely difficult to read."},{"time":241000,"text":"But all I have to do is"},{"time":243000,"text":"fill certain areas of those letterforms"},{"time":246000,"text":"and I can bring those words out of"},{"time":248000,"text":"the background pattern."},{"time":250000,"text":"But maybe that's a little too obvious."},{"time":252000,"text":"So then I can add some color in with the background"},{"time":255000,"text":"and add a bit more color in with the words themselves,"},{"time":258000,"text":"and this way, working with the art director,"},{"time":260000,"text":"I'm able to bring it to just the right point"},{"time":263000,"text":"that it's puzzling for the audience --"},{"time":266000,"text":"they can figure out that there's something they have to read --"},{"time":268000,"text":"but it's not impossible for them to read."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"I'm also interested in working with"},{"time":275000,"text":"unusual materials"},{"time":277000,"text":"and common materials in unusual ways."},{"time":280000,"text":"So this requires figuring out how to"},{"time":282000,"text":"get the most out of something's innate properties"},{"time":285000,"text":"and also how to bend it to my will."},{"time":287000,"text":"So ultimately,"},{"time":289000,"text":"my goal is to create something unexpected."},{"time":294000,"text":"To this end, I have worked in sugar"},{"time":296000,"text":"for Stefan Sagmeister,"},{"time":298000,"text":"three-time TED speaker."},{"time":300000,"text":"And this project began essentially"},{"time":302000,"text":"on my kitchen table."},{"time":304000,"text":"I've been eating cereal for breakfast"},{"time":306000,"text":"all of my life."},{"time":308000,"text":"And for that same amount of time,"},{"time":310000,"text":"I've been spilling sugar on the table"},{"time":312000,"text":"and just kind of playing with it with my fingers."},{"time":315000,"text":"And eventually I used this technique"},{"time":317000,"text":"to create a piece of artwork."},{"time":319000,"text":"And then I used it again to create"},{"time":321000,"text":"six pieces for Stefan's book,"},{"time":323000,"text":"\"Things in My Life I've Learned So Far.\""},{"time":326000,"text":"And these were created"},{"time":328000,"text":"without sketches, just freehand,"},{"time":330000,"text":"by putting the sugar down on a white surface"},{"time":332000,"text":"and then manipulating it to get"},{"time":334000,"text":"the words and designs out of it."},{"time":337000,"text":"Recently, I've also made some"},{"time":339000,"text":"rather highbrow baroque borders"},{"time":341000,"text":"out of lowbrow pasta."},{"time":343000,"text":"And this is for a chapter that I'm doing in a book,"},{"time":346000,"text":"and the chapter is on honor."},{"time":348000,"text":"So it's a little bit unexpected,"},{"time":350000,"text":"but, in a way, it refers"},{"time":352000,"text":"to the macaroni art"},{"time":354000,"text":"that children make for their parents"},{"time":356000,"text":"or they make in school and give to their parents,"},{"time":358000,"text":"which is in itself a form of honor."},{"time":362000,"text":"This is what you can do with some household tinfoil."},{"time":367000,"text":"Okay, well, it's what I can do with some household tinfoil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376000,"text":"I'm very interested in wonder,"},{"time":379000,"text":"in design as an impetus to inquiring."},{"time":383000,"text":"To say I wonder is to say"},{"time":385000,"text":"I question, I ask."},{"time":387000,"text":"And to experience wonder is to experience awe."},{"time":391000,"text":"So I'm currently working on a book,"},{"time":393000,"text":"which plays with both senses of the word,"},{"time":395000,"text":"as I explore some of my own ideas"},{"time":397000,"text":"and inquiries"},{"time":399000,"text":"in a visual display of rather"},{"time":401000,"text":"peacock-like grandeur."},{"time":404000,"text":"The world is full of wonder."},{"time":406000,"text":"But the world of graphic design,"},{"time":409000,"text":"for the most part, is not."},{"time":411000,"text":"So I'm using my own writings"},{"time":413000,"text":"as a kind of testing ground for a book that has"},{"time":415000,"text":"an interdependency between word and image"},{"time":418000,"text":"as a kind of seductive force."},{"time":421000,"text":"I think that one of the things"},{"time":423000,"text":"that religions got right"},{"time":425000,"text":"was the use of visual wonder"},{"time":427000,"text":"to deliver a message."},{"time":429000,"text":"I think this true marriage of art and information"},{"time":432000,"text":"is woefully underused in adult literature,"},{"time":435000,"text":"and I'm mystified as to"},{"time":437000,"text":"why visual wealth is not more commonly used"},{"time":440000,"text":"to enhance intellectual wealth."},{"time":443000,"text":"When we look at works like this,"},{"time":445000,"text":"we tend to associate them with children's literature."},{"time":448000,"text":"There's an implication that ornamental graphics"},{"time":451000,"text":"detract from the seriousness of the content."},{"time":454000,"text":"But I really hope to have the opportunity"},{"time":456000,"text":"to change that perception."},{"time":459000,"text":"This book is taking rather a long time,"},{"time":463000,"text":"but I'm nearly done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466000,"text":"For some reason, I thought it would be a good idea"},{"time":468000,"text":"to put an intermission"},{"time":470000,"text":"in my talk."},{"time":472000,"text":"And this is it -- just to give you and me a moment to catch up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":483000,"text":"So I do these valentines."},{"time":486000,"text":"I've been sending out valentines"},{"time":488000,"text":"on a fairly large scale since 2005."},{"time":491000,"text":"These are my valentines"},{"time":493000,"text":"from 2005 and 2006."},{"time":495000,"text":"And I started by"},{"time":497000,"text":"doing just a single image like this"},{"time":499000,"text":"and sending them out to each person."},{"time":501000,"text":"But in 2007,"},{"time":503000,"text":"I got the cockamamie idea"},{"time":505000,"text":"to hand-draw each valentine"},{"time":508000,"text":"for everyone on my mailing list."},{"time":511000,"text":"I reduced my mailing list to 150 people."},{"time":515000,"text":"And I drew each person"},{"time":517000,"text":"their own unique valentine"},{"time":520000,"text":"and put their name on it"},{"time":522000,"text":"and numbered it and signed it and sent it out."},{"time":524000,"text":"Believe it or not, I devised this"},{"time":526000,"text":"as a timesaving method."},{"time":530000,"text":"I was very busy in the beginning of that year,"},{"time":532000,"text":"and I didn't know when I was going to find time"},{"time":534000,"text":"to design and print a single valentine."},{"time":537000,"text":"And I thought that I could kind of do this piecemeal"},{"time":539000,"text":"as I was traveling."},{"time":542000,"text":"It didn't exactly work out that way."},{"time":545000,"text":"There's a longer story to this,"},{"time":547000,"text":"but I did get them all done in time,"},{"time":550000,"text":"and they were extremely well received."},{"time":553000,"text":"I got an almost 100 percent response rate."},{"time":555000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":557000,"text":"And those who didn't respond"},{"time":559000,"text":"will never receive anything from me ever again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":567000,"text":"Last year,"},{"time":569000,"text":"I took a more conceptual approach to the valentine."},{"time":572000,"text":"I had this idea that I wanted people"},{"time":574000,"text":"to receive a kind of"},{"time":577000,"text":"mysterious love letter,"},{"time":579000,"text":"like a found fragment in their mailbox."},{"time":582000,"text":"I wanted it to be something"},{"time":584000,"text":"that was not addressed to them"},{"time":586000,"text":"or signed by me,"},{"time":588000,"text":"something that caused them to wonder"},{"time":590000,"text":"what on Earth this thing was."},{"time":593000,"text":"And I specifically wrote"},{"time":595000,"text":"four pages that don't connect."},{"time":598000,"text":"There were four different versions of this."},{"time":600000,"text":"And I wrote them"},{"time":602000,"text":"so that they begin in the middle of a sentence,"},{"time":604000,"text":"end in the middle of a sentence."},{"time":606000,"text":"And they're on the one hand, universal,"},{"time":609000,"text":"so I avoid specific names or places,"},{"time":612000,"text":"but on the other hand, they're personal."},{"time":614000,"text":"So I wanted people to really get the sense that"},{"time":617000,"text":"they had received something that could have been"},{"time":619000,"text":"a love letter to them."},{"time":621000,"text":"And I'm just going to read one of them to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624000,"text":"\"You've never really been sure of this,"},{"time":627000,"text":"but I can assure you that this quirk"},{"time":629000,"text":"you're so self-conscious of"},{"time":631000,"text":"is intensely endearing."},{"time":633000,"text":"Just please accept that this piece of you"},{"time":635000,"text":"escapes with your smile,"},{"time":637000,"text":"and those of us who notice"},{"time":639000,"text":"are happy to catch it in passing."},{"time":641000,"text":"Time spent with you is like chasing and catching small birds,"},{"time":644000,"text":"but without the scratches and bird shit.\""},{"time":646000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":648000,"text":"\"That is to say,"},{"time":650000,"text":"your thoughts and words flit and dart,"},{"time":652000,"text":"disconcertedly elusive at times,"},{"time":654000,"text":"but when caught and examined --"},{"time":656000,"text":"ahh, such a wonder,"},{"time":658000,"text":"such a delightful reward."},{"time":660000,"text":"There's no passing time with you,"},{"time":662000,"text":"only collecting --"},{"time":664000,"text":"the collecting of moments with the hope for preservation"},{"time":666000,"text":"and at the same time release."},{"time":669000,"text":"Impossible? I don't think so."},{"time":671000,"text":"I know this makes you embarrassed."},{"time":673000,"text":"I'm certain I can see you blushing."},{"time":675000,"text":"But I just have to tell you because"},{"time":677000,"text":"sometimes I hear your self-doubt,"},{"time":679000,"text":"and it's so crushing to think"},{"time":681000,"text":"that you may not know how truly wonderful you are,"},{"time":683000,"text":"how inspiring and delightful"},{"time":686000,"text":"and really, truly the most completely ...\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":689000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":691000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"So Valentine's Day"},{"time":699000,"text":"is coming up in a couple of days,"},{"time":701000,"text":"and these are currently arriving"},{"time":703000,"text":"in mailboxes all around the world."},{"time":706000,"text":"This year, I got, what I really have to say"},{"time":708000,"text":"is a rather brilliant idea,"},{"time":711000,"text":"to laser cut"},{"time":714000,"text":"my valentines"},{"time":716000,"text":"out of used Christmas cards."},{"time":719000,"text":"So I solicited friends"},{"time":721000,"text":"to send me their used Christmas cards,"},{"time":724000,"text":"and I made 500 of these."},{"time":727000,"text":"Each one of them is completely different."},{"time":729000,"text":"I'm just really, really thrilled with them."},{"time":731000,"text":"I don't have that much else to say,"},{"time":735000,"text":"but they turned out really well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"I do spend a lot of time on my work."},{"time":743000,"text":"And one of the things that I've been thinking about recently"},{"time":746000,"text":"is what is worth while."},{"time":748000,"text":"What is it that's worth spending my time on"},{"time":750000,"text":"and my life on in this way?"},{"time":753000,"text":"Working in the commercial world,"},{"time":755000,"text":"this is something that I do have to struggle with at times."},{"time":759000,"text":"And yes, sometimes I'm swayed by money."},{"time":762000,"text":"But ultimately, I don't consider that a worthy goal."},{"time":765000,"text":"What makes something worthwhile for me"},{"time":768000,"text":"is the people I work for or with,"},{"time":771000,"text":"the conditions I work under"},{"time":773000,"text":"and the audience that I'm able to reach."},{"time":776000,"text":"So I might ask: \"Who is it for?\""},{"time":778000,"text":"\"What does it say?\""},{"time":780000,"text":"and \"What does it do?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":783000,"text":"You know, I have to tell you, it's really difficult"},{"time":786000,"text":"for someone like me to come up on stage"},{"time":789000,"text":"at this conference"},{"time":791000,"text":"with these unbelievably brilliant minds,"},{"time":794000,"text":"who are thinking these"},{"time":796000,"text":"really big-picture,"},{"time":798000,"text":"world-changing, life-changing"},{"time":801000,"text":"ideas and technologies."},{"time":806000,"text":"And it's very, very common"},{"time":809000,"text":"for designers and people in the visual arts"},{"time":812000,"text":"to feel that we're"},{"time":814000,"text":"not contributing enough,"},{"time":817000,"text":"or worse, that all we're doing is"},{"time":819000,"text":"contributing to landfill."},{"time":821000,"text":"Here I am; I'm showing you"},{"time":823000,"text":"some pretty visuals"},{"time":825000,"text":"and talking about aesthetics."},{"time":829000,"text":"But I've come to believe that"},{"time":831000,"text":"truly imaginative visual work"},{"time":834000,"text":"is extremely important in society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":837000,"text":"Just in the way that I'm inspired"},{"time":839000,"text":"by books"},{"time":841000,"text":"and magazines of all kinds,"},{"time":843000,"text":"conversations I have, movies,"},{"time":846000,"text":"so I also think,"},{"time":848000,"text":"when I put visual work out there into the mass media,"},{"time":851000,"text":"work that is interesting, unusual,"},{"time":854000,"text":"intriguing,"},{"time":856000,"text":"work that maybe opens up that sense"},{"time":858000,"text":"of inquiry in the mind,"},{"time":861000,"text":"that I'm seeding the imagination of the populace."},{"time":865000,"text":"And you just never know who"},{"time":867000,"text":"is going to take something from that"},{"time":869000,"text":"and turn it into something else,"},{"time":872000,"text":"because inspiration"},{"time":874000,"text":"is cross-pollinating."},{"time":876000,"text":"So a piece of mine"},{"time":878000,"text":"may inspire a playwright"},{"time":880000,"text":"or a novelist or a scientist,"},{"time":883000,"text":"and that in turn may be the seed"},{"time":886000,"text":"that inspires a doctor"},{"time":888000,"text":"or a philanthropist"},{"time":890000,"text":"or a babysitter."},{"time":892000,"text":"And this isn't something that you can quantify"},{"time":894000,"text":"or track or measure,"},{"time":897000,"text":"and we tend to undervalue things in society"},{"time":899000,"text":"that we can't measure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":901000,"text":"But I really believe"},{"time":903000,"text":"that a fully operating, rich society"},{"time":906000,"text":"needs these seeds coming from all directions"},{"time":908000,"text":"and all disciplines"},{"time":910000,"text":"in order to keep the gears of inspiration"},{"time":913000,"text":"and imagination"},{"time":915000,"text":"flowing and cycling and growing."},{"time":920000,"text":"So that's why I do what I do,"},{"time":923000,"text":"and why I spend so much time and effort on it,"},{"time":927000,"text":"and why I work in the commercial, public sphere,"},{"time":930000,"text":"as opposed to the isolated, private sphere"},{"time":933000,"text":"of fine art:"},{"time":935000,"text":"because I want as many people as possible"},{"time":938000,"text":"to see my work, notice it, be drawn into it,"},{"time":941000,"text":"and be able to take something from it."},{"time":944000,"text":"And I actually really feel that it's worthwhile"},{"time":947000,"text":"to spend my valuable"},{"time":949000,"text":"and limited time on this Earth"},{"time":951000,"text":"in this way."},{"time":953000,"text":"And I thank you for allowing me to show it to you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":956000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}